issues.body:
Now there is an implementation of Usage named `OpenAiUsage` 

```
public class OpenAiUsage implements Usage {

	public static OpenAiUsage from(OpenAiApi.Usage usage) {
		return new OpenAiUsage(usage);
	}

	private final OpenAiApi.Usage usage;
```

This should not contain the Azure SDK class as a private field member.  DefaultUsage should be used instead.

See #814 for some original context on this issue.
